info.title: DarkCube
info.author: NoNameNo
info.details:
Another New production to promote GRRLIB (http://GRRLIB.SANTO.FR) and to show that this is not only a simple 2D lib, but also a nice, simple, and powerfull 3D lib with objects rendering, texture, lightsources, etc... and all done by GX.

Special thanks to Crayon
